  "prompt": "I had crush on my classmate, we used to talk a lot. But now we hardly talk to each other. Should I tell him that I loved him?",
  "response": "Here are some things to consider before deciding:\n\n1. Current situation\n\u2022 How is your relationship now?\n\u2022 Are you still friends or distant?\n\n2. Potential outcomes\n\u2022 Positive: He might feel the same way\n\u2022 Negative: He might not reciprocate, causing awkwardness\n\n3. Considerations before confessing\n\u2022 Is he single?\n\u2022 Are you ready for any possible response?\n\u2022 Will this affect your friendship/social circle?\n\n4. Recommended approach\n\u2022 Start by rebuilding communication\n\u2022 Gauge his interest and current feelings\n\u2022 If comfortable, have an honest conversation\n\u2022 Be prepared for any outcome\n\u2022 Maintain respect for his feelings\n\n5. Alternative options\n\u2022 Remain friends\n\u2022 Move on\n\u2022 Stay open to possibilities\n\nUltimately, the decision is personal. Trust your instincts and be prepared for different responses.\n\nWould you like to discuss this further?",
